wikipedia_page.main: Ava Kuyken (born 15 June 2001) is an English footballer who plays as a midfielder for Bristol City in the FA Women's Championship. Previously she played for FA WSL club Arsenal for two seasons, 2017–18 and 2018–19. From 2019 to 2021 she was on a collegiate scholarship at the University of Florida with the Florida Gators women's soccer.
